By using a loop node, you can perform th: By using a loop node, you can perform the same operation on multiple sets of data. The source of these sets can be either multiple records from a query node or multiple associated records of a single record. Loop node can also be used for iterating a certain number of times or for looping through each character in a string. However, excessive looping may cause performance issues, so use with caution.
